snippet.title: A Puzzle Game About Graph Theory??
snippet.description:
Graphomata, totally free and highly polished. But I'm not sure about its interestingness and depth so far - optimization puzzle games tend to take a while before the optimization aspect gets interesting. I hope it does!

https://graphomata.com/game/play-online.html

Short games playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLg5Ta3CWcYX4X-lxcjqnig5Do-qXYNBt7


"secret" discord: https://discord.gg/V64JDvbWsf
